{"tid":1418272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[勿分化]呢場運動係一幅磚牆，市民係磚，前線係水泥","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:46:58.000Z","uid":299865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d47c11d470b2b595d53f8c22bead592b196d9920","tid":1418272,"uid":299865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先感謝各位前線努力。<br />\n但你屌我係P牌我都要講。市民係磚，前線係水泥，加埋先係一幅穩固嘅牆。只係不斷堆水泥或不斷砌磚幅牆都會散。懇請各位前線抖一抖，週末再集合，等文宣煲大黑警同林鄭啲惡行先出師有名。</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"af8aacbd7551b4c46d677d1b38ac11bb13cbe636","tid":1418272,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:19:25.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割蓆<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418188</a>"},{"pid":"9fc7f52fe2ca13d257ade86f1ac886adcb72f44b","tid":1418272,"uid":299865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:39.000Z","msg":"出核彈都要有和理非回合。唔好唔記得一直係要輪住做先行到呢步。"},{"pid":"97758d4fa34f0c0bb04497f3dc6731feaea29f02","tid":1418272,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:37:15.000Z","msg":"人地搵命博,請討論下一步,<br />\n唔係心理輔導影相俾前線鬧。<br />\n和理非請合作支援前線,幫前線擋住同解釋影相既後果<br />\n和理非都要識進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出核彈都唔同前線割"},{"pid":"b72448c5983dc7c65eba8cf6efc095bd89eae6f6","tid":1418272,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:46:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">面對惡法暴政仲可以和平理性真係唔易</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}